Package: mediateSWCRT
Title: Mediation Analysis in a Stepped Wedge Cluster Randomized Trials
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Zhiqiang Cao; Fan Li
Maintainer: Zhiqiang Cao <zcaoae@connect.ust.hk>
Description: Functions for calculating the point and interval estimates of the natural indirect effect (NIE), natural direct effect (NDE), total effect (TE), and mediation proportion (MP) in a stepped wedge cluster randomized trials with a constant treatment effect or time-dependent treatment effect. We perform the methods considered in Cao and Li (2024) Mediation analysis in stepped wedge cluster randomized trials.
License: GPL
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports: lme4,stats
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
NeedsCompilation: no
Packaged: 2024-04-03 02:50:48 UTC; user
